# OpenCode Premium UI/UX Configuration
# ==========================================
# 🎉 GOOD NEWS: Most API keys are OPTIONAL!
# ==========================================
#
# OpenCode provides FREE access to these models (no API key needed):
# - MiniMax 2.5 ⭐ RECOMMENDED (fast & good for coding)
# - Mistral Small 3.1 24B
# - Nvidia Llama 3.1 Nemotron 70B Super ⭐ BEST QUALITY
# - Kimi K2
# - GLM 4
# - Mistral Nemo
#
# Only the 21st.dev Magic MCP requires an API key for premium components.

# ==========================================
# REQUIRED (Only this one!)
# ==========================================

# 21st.dev Magic (For AI component generation - like v0.dev)
# Get your FREE key at: https://21st.dev/magic/console
# This unlocks 20+ layouts, 35+ components, 19 animations
TWENTY_FIRST_DEV_API_KEY=your-21st-dev-api-key-here

# ==========================================
# OPTIONAL: Paid AI Providers (NOT NEEDED!)
# ==========================================
# Leave these empty or commented to use FREE OpenCode models

# Anthropic Claude (Optional - paid)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-your-key-here

# OpenAI (Optional - paid)
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-proj-your-key-here

# Groq (Optional - paid but cheap)
# GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_your_key_here

# OpenRouter (Optional - some models free)
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-your-key-here

# ==========================================
# OPTIONAL: Other Services
# ==========================================

# GitHub Token (for Copilot models - optional)
# GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_your_token_here

# Google Vertex AI (optional)
# VERTEXAI_PROJECT=your-gcp-project-id
# VERTEXAI_LOCATION=us-central1
# GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key

# AWS Bedrock (optional)
# AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your-access-key
# AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=your-secret-key
# AWS_REGION=us-east-1

# Azure OpenAI (optional)
# AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT=https://your-resource.openai.azure.com
# AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY=your-azure-key
# AZURE_OPENAI_API_VERSION=2024-02-01

# ==========================================
# DEVELOPMENT SETTINGS
# ==========================================

# Default shell (adjust for your system)
SHELL=/bin/bash

# Node environment
NODE_ENV=development

# Debug mode (set to true for verbose logging)
DEBUG=false

# ==========================================
# 💡 QUICK START
# ==========================================
# 1. Only fill in TWENTY_FIRST_DEV_API_KEY
# 2. Leave everything else blank
# 3. OpenCode will use FREE models automatically
# 4. Build amazing websites at zero cost!